Objects:
    -----------------------------------------
       RA   (2000)   DE    Designation(s)
    -----------------------------------------
        00.00        +00.00   Mock stellar sample

Abstract:
  This is a mock stellar catalogue generated to test the ARTE CDS table
  generation tools.


Description:
  The table contains mock stellar identifiers, spectral types, distances,
  rotation periods, bolometric luminosities, habitable-zone distances, and X-ray
  luminosities. The values are intended only for software testing.


